Where to begin… Thank you to everyone who helped me reach this goal. To my family for always encouraging to pursue my dreams, I love you immensely and  I’m so thankful to have you there at the ceremony. To the friends I made in the program (you know who you are 💛) thank you for reminding me to take breaks when the stress got to me. The girl who originally wanted to go to florida for school probably would’ve missed out on some of the best years of my life. College was crazy, hard, fun, and now I’m ready for this next chapter of my life. 🎓❣️
